       in captions is formatted.  Use \"1\" for numerals, \"a\"
       for alphabets etc.

  - `:entity-name' :: a string.  This qualifies captions on
       export.

  - `:caption-style' :: a string.  This is the paragraph style
       used for typesetting the captions.

See `org-odt-format-label'.")

